node.text:
⁣
⁣
The big THIRTY TWO 👨🏽‍🦳 I hope you have the best day (that is inevitable because I’m cooking a breakfast and dinner for you) and that you enjoy this little compilation as much as I enjoyed putting it together! Thank you for being you, you’re the best and I can’t wait to make many more fun memories together until we are rocking in our rocking chairs 😝! I love you millionssssss ♥️🥰

Take your training to the next level with our Extreme workouts, now available for the gym and home on the Strongandsxy fitness app!

No matter your level of fitness, we have a plan for you! Click the link in our bio to take advantage of our 50% OFF subscriptions SALE. 💥 

www.strongandsxy.com

#StrongandSxy 💪🏼💗
#StrongandSxyApp
#getfitwithStrongandSxy
#homeworkouts
#fitnessjourney

OUTFIT: @gymshark

⁣⁣
🔸 50% off ALL subscription prices for the @strongandsxy fitness app AND the home workout guides. Once you pay this discounted price for the Strong&Sxy fitness app, that’s what you’ll continue to pay so it’s a great time to get a subscription! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
🔴 IMPORTANT:⁣⁣
YOU WILL ONLY GET THE 50% DISCOUNT FOR THE @STRONGANDSXY FITNESS APP VIA OUR WEBSITE STRONGANDSXY.COM YOU WILL NOT GET THE DISCOUNT VIA THE APP STORE!!! PLEASE PLEASE TAKE NOTE OF THIS! 🙏🏼⁣⁣
⁣⁣
✖️MY RECOMMENDATION:⁣⁣
I would advise to go for the @strongandsxy fitness app as it is completely CUSTOMISABLE to you. You receive a meal plan and a training plan and there are LOTS of amazing features to enjoy. Plus we work hard to evolve the app month on month 💪🏼⁣⁣
⁣⁣
🔸15% discount on the long @strongandsxy resistance bands with code STRONG15⁣⁣
⁣⁣
I really hope this helps some of⁣⁣
you stay active. I want to try and help you guys as much as possible while you’re at home. It’s important that we look after our mental health. Going to the gym is our happy place and gives us something to focus on ... well that doesn’t have to stop now! 😊💗⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Sending lots of love & positive vibes your way ✨🤗

node.text:
Jamaica 🇯🇲 last year, he had such an amazing aura about him, his message touched our hearts 🥺♥️ ⁣
⁣
Hopefully change will come and one day we can all live in love and unity! 🙏🏼 We have a responsibility to eradicate racism and we need to keep on speaking up to help towards making a change. It’s so upsetting to see what is going on 🥺. But seeing everyone spreading awareness and now taking action towards being anti-racist in their own way (something I am definitely leaning more and more about the last week, there are so many things I didn’t know, it’s really opened my eyes 🙈😭 but I’m working on it) and not just ‘not racist’ is amazing to see. Actions speak louder than words! Racism isn’t born it’s taught and that needs to stop now ✋🏼 We have to use our voices and take real action to make a sustainable change towards equality, fair laws and justice ! It’s insane that this shit is still going on in 2020, what the actual F!! We should be judged on the content of our hearts and not the colour of our skin. The real change most definitely starts from within ♥️ Like @ohhappydani illustration says ‘Until you fix it here ➞ ♥️, and address it here ➞ 🏠, nothing will change here ➞ 🌍’ ⁣
⁣
There should only be one race and that’s the human race 🙏🏼✊🏻✊🏼✊🏽✊🏾✊🏿♥️
#blacklivesmatter

node.text:
HOW TO DEADLIFT ✅ ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
When I first started weightlifting, the deadlift was an exercise that intimidated me. It has various movements all in one movement 😅 It’s another exercise that you’ll need to play around with foot positioning to see what suits your body’s anatomy, because we are all different and what works for someone else might not work for you. I’ve written what’s on screen below incase it went too fast. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
One tip: Set your phone up to record yourself to check your form. It’s the best way! 📱🤳 ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
⁣⁣
1 Have your feet around shoulder width apart & line up the bar over the middle of your feet. You can have your toes slightly flared or straight ahead. Play around and see what works best for you ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
2 Grip the bar with your hands placed just outside of your legs and push your knees into your elbow creases⁣⁣
⁣⁣
3 Sit your hips back until your hips are positioned between your knees and shoulders. raise your chest and depress your shoulder blades (pull them downward) to keep everything tight (this bit is important❗️)⁣⁣
⁣⁣
4  Take a deep breath, brace your core and push through your heels to execute (think about pushing the floor awayyyy) while keeping the bar close ... and execute ! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
5  Sit your hips back while lowering the bar down and keep your shins vertical & repeat ⁣
⁣
OUTFIT: @gymshark

node.text:
Here’s what went down in our push seshhhh! 💪🏼 working our shoulders/chest & triceps (forgot to film my tri exercises but noted it below)⁣⁣
⁣⁣
I currently have 25% off all app subscriptions on my @strongandsxy fitness app via strongandsxy.com (not the App Store) Lets get STRONG & SXY! 💫 ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
(This isn’t the order of my videos FYI but this is the order to do them in starting with compounds first) ⁣⁣
Bench press 3 x 6-8⁣⁣
Incline bench press 3 x 6-8⁣⁣
Machine shoulder press 3 x 8-10⁣⁣
DB lat raise 3 x 15,10,15 ⁣⁣
DB Front raises 10 neutral (palms facing in) 10 overhand - straight through ! ⁣⁣
Cable standing crucifix lat raises 3 x 12⁣⁣
Tricep rope push down - 2 x 30⁣⁣
⁣⁣
I like to use resistance bands on my bench presses as it helps reduce the weight at the bottom when my shoulder joints are at their most vulnerable. It’s still really difficult throughout the movement because you still have the load as you descend and ascend. Game changer ! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Wearing new @gymshark animal shorts (not released yet) 👀 Are you fan? Coz I’m a fan!! 🤩

node.text:
Wowow!! @m1ssngo_fit has been on her health & fitness journey on my @strongandsxy fitness app for 1 year & 6 months and these are her results. It’s a process and it doesn’t happen overnight but Kim has been consistent, dedicated and patient! I’m so proud of her for being committed and changing her lifestyle. ⁣
⁣⁣
Please remember there are so many health benefits to losing weight (not just what you look like on the outside) and those are what’s going to make all the difference for your future self 💫 ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Confidence comes from within. When you feel good on the inside you radiate on the outside. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Swipe to see what Kim had to say 🥰⁣
⁣
You can download my @strongandsxy fitness app and enjoy 14 days for free by visiting strongandsxy.com. It’ll provide you with a structured meal & training plan so you don’t have to think about anything ! 💫
